# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# A PyQt interface for uploading files to Shotgun.
# 
# Allows you to configure the app for a specific shotgun instance and directory 
# structure. Uploaded files need to be linked to an existing entity, but can 
# have notes and tags applied.
# 
# Requires your Shotgun instance have API access to the Attachment entity
# which is not on by default as of v2.0.3
# 
# Author: Rob Blau <rblau@laika.com>
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
